PrecisEnactment of an ORDER RESPECTING THE WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (KLUANE FIRST NATION, Y.T.) - which (a) provides for the withdrawal from disposal of a number of tracts of land in the Yukon Territory until August 31, 2006, and (b) repeals the Withdrawal from Disposal Order made by Order in Council P.C. 1999-462.
